The Shadow of the Wind by Carlos Ruiz Zafón belongs to a 4 book series called &ldquo;The Cemetery of Forgotten Books&rdquo;
Rating: 10/10 Review The story of this book is recreated in Barcelona around 1930&rsquo;s - 1950&rsquo;s, and it&rsquo;s about the life of a boy who love books and thanks to his father he discovered a book that he is totally enchanted with.
Over the story he tries to discover more about the author, his life and where is he along with why he cannot find more copies of his books around.
